{"id":94,"name":"الشرح","transliteration":"Ash-Sharh","translation":"开拓","type":"meccan","total_verses":8,"verses":[{"id":1,"text":"أَلَمۡ نَشۡرَحۡ لَكَ صَدۡرَكَ","translation":"难道我没有为你而开拓你的胸襟吗？","transliteration":"Alam nashrah laka sadraka"},{"id":2,"text":"وَوَضَعۡنَا عَنكَ وِزۡرَكَ","translation":"我卸下了你的重任，","transliteration":"WawadaAAna AAanka wizraka"},{"id":3,"text":"ٱلَّذِيٓ أَنقَضَ ظَهۡرَكَ","translation":"即使你的背担负过重的，","transliteration":"Allathee anqada thahraka"},{"id":4,"text":"وَرَفَعۡنَا لَكَ ذِكۡرَكَ","translation":"而提高了你的声望，","transliteration":"WarafaAAna laka thikraka"},{"id":5,"text":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرًا","translation":"与艰难相伴的，确是容易，","transliteration":"Fainna maAAa alAAusri yusran"},{"id":6,"text":"إِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرٗا","translation":"与艰难相伴的，确是容易，","transliteration":"Inna maAAa alAAusri yusran"},{"id":7,"text":"فَإِذَا فَرَغۡتَ فَٱنصَبۡ","translation":"当你的事务完毕时，","transliteration":"Faitha faraghta fainsab"},{"id":8,"text":"وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَٱرۡغَب","translation":"你应当勤劳，你应当向你的主恳求。","transliteration":"Waila rabbika fairghab"}]}
